commit.title: [ci] [gitlab] Add tags for fast runner selection + increase parallelism.
commit.message:
[ci] [gitlab] Add tags for fast runner selection + increase parallelism.

We make `build` and `ci-flambda` templates to use 4 jobs and a
`fast-runner` tag in order to improve latency.
